# ğŸ¥ i_dawa_app â€” AI Pharmacy Management System

**i_dawa_app** is a lightweight, offline-friendly pharmacy management system built with **Streamlit** and **SQLite**, designed for small and growing pharmacies.

It combines **inventory management, sales, purchases, reports, barcode support**, and a **built-in AI assistant (Dawa AI)** to make daily pharmacy operations faster and safer.

